oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Songwriter Session - Ashley Gorley and Rodney Clawson - 2015-05-23
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Performance by singer songwriters Ashley Gorley and Rodney Clawson from the Ford Theater at the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum on May 23, 2015. In support of the exhibit Luke Bryan: Dirt Road Diary.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Ashley Gorley; Rodney Clawson;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: Includes questions from the audience. Performances include; Crash My Party (Rodney Clawson) -- I See You (Ashley Gorley) -- Sweet Southern Comfort (Rodney Clawson -- That's My Kind Of Night (Ashley Gorley) -- Drunk On You (Rodney Clawson) -- Games (Ashley Gorley) -- Fast (Rodney Clawson) -- Play It Again (Ashley Gorley).
